(24, 'about.content', '{\"has_image\":\"1\",\"title\":\"About Us\",\"heading\":\"Creating Payment Channel In Global Market !!\",\"button_text\":\"Get Started\",\"button_link\":\"register\",\"description\":\"\\u201cMonocard\\u201d is stored on your phone and can be used to pay contactless in stores or online, but has its own unique card number, expiry date, and CVC.\\n\\u201cdigital card\\u201d is a copy of your physical bank card that\\u2019s stored on your phone. Digital cards have the same card number, expiry date, and CVC as your physical bank card, and can be used with Apple Pay or Google Pay. A \\u201cdisposable card\\u201d is a virtual card that can only be used once. Once you\\u2019ve paid, the card details can\\u2019t be used again.\",\"image\":\"62547b30cec581649703728.png\"}', 0, '2020-10-28 00:51:20', '2022-04-11 19:02:09'),
